    {
      "paragraph_name": "COPAU0A",
      "summary": null,
      "purpose": "This paragraph defines the BMS map COPAU0A, which represents the layout of the 'View Authorizations' screen. It specifies the screen's dimensions (SIZE=(24,80)), starting position (COLUMN=1, LINE=1), and contains definitions for various fields displayed on the screen. These fields include labels (e.g., 'Tran:', 'Date:', 'Prog:', 'Time:', 'Search Acct Id:'), input fields (ACCTID), and output fields displaying customer information (CNAME, CUSTID, ADDR001, ADDR002, PHONE1, ACCSTAT) and transaction details (TRNID01-TRNID05, PDATE01-PDATE05, PTIME01-PTIME05, PTYPE01-PTYPE05, PAPRV01-PAPRV04, PSTAT01-PSTAT04, PAMT001-PAMT004). The map defines the attributes of each field, such as color, highlighting, and protection status. The map serves as a template for displaying data and receiving input from the user. It does not contain any processing logic but defines the visual representation of the screen.",
